# Nusxa: android/firebase_secrets.properties (gitda yo'q) va defaultWebClientId ni to'ldiring.
# Bu satr reCAPTCHA / Email ro'yxatdan o'tish uchun "Web" OAuth identifikatoridir.
#
# Buni topish: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials?project=geofield-pro-8529f
#  - "OAuth 2.0 Client IDs" ro'yxatida: "Web client (auto created by Google Service)" yoki
#    "Web client (auto created by Firebase)" → Client ID (oxirida .apps.googleusercontent.com).
# Agar "Web" bo'lmasa: Firebase → Authentication → Sign-in method → Google → yoqish →
#    5-10 daqiqadan so'ng yana Credentials sahifasiga qarang.
#
# Muqobil: muhit o'zgaruvchisi FIREBASE_DEFAULT_WEB_CLIENT_ID
#
defaultWebClientId=
